	<Language_en_US>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_NIGHTMARE_MOON_DEFEATED_1">
			<Text>Sister, plea...se....he...l..p....me....</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_NIGHTMARE_MOON_DEFEATED_2">
			<Text>I'll be back, even if its another thousand years!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_NIGHTMARE_MOON_EXPANSION_SERIOUS_WARNING_1">
			<Text>You dare claim my land? The night shall decend upon you ever so quickly if you choose to continue.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_NIGHTMARE_MOON_FIRSTGREETING_1">
			<Text>Greetings, I am Nightmare Moon, Princess of the Night and ruler of Equestria. Have you come to profess your love of my beautiful night? </Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_NIGHTMARE_MOON_GREETING_HOSTILE_HELLO_1">
			<Text>As a future subject of mine, you should learn to kneel.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_NIGHTMARE_MOON_GREETING_NEUTRAL_HELLO_1">
			<Text>What is it, I am quite busy tormenting my sister.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_NIGHTMARE_MOON_GREETING_POLITE_HELLO_1">
			<Text>Welcome child of the night. It is always a pleasure to see you.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_NIGHTMARE_MOON_HOSTILE_AGGRESSIVE_MILITARY_WARNING_1">
			<Text>How will your troops fight in the dead of night? I will have them jumping at shadows unless you remove them.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_NIGHTMARE_MOON_OPEN_BORDERS_EXCHANGE_1">
			<Text>Let us open our boarders and enjoy the night together.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_NIGHTMARE_MOON_RESPONSE_REQUEST_1">
			<Text>The night requires your assistance. Your kindness would not go unnoticed.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_NIGHTMARE_MOON_LUXURY_TRADE_1">
			<Text>It would seem I have aquired an abundance of goods. Do you care to trade? Would this work? I don't have my abacus on me.</Text>
		</Row>
	</Language_en_US>


