		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CIVILOPEDIA_LEADERS_NIGHTMARE_MOON_TEXT_1">
			<Text>Long ago there lived two sisters that shared rulership of Equestria. The eldest governed the sun, the younger governed the moon. The citizens of Equestria worked and played in the day, but slept at night. Over time the younger sister grew jealous of the love her eldest sister recieved. The bitterness grew in her until she trandsformed into Nightmare Moon. She took control of the skies, casting Equestria in eternal darkness. Celestia, with the power of the elements of harmony, defeated her and banished her to the moon. After a thousand years, the stars aided Nightmare Moon in escaping, plunging Equestria in eternal night once again. </Text>
		</Row>
